{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-jsx","path":"/deep-js-23/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"ocean.dev"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"b7bdbe02-c25a-5449-a2b0-10c6c18a5e6d","excerpt":"🔥 실행컨텍스트: 자바스크립트의 동작원리를 담고 있는 핵심 개념 실행컨텍스트를 이해하면, 자바스크립트가 스코프를 기반으로 식별자와 식별자에 바인딩된 값(식별자 바인딩)을 관리하는 방식과\n이 발생하는 이유, 의 동작 방식, 그리고 와 함께 동작하는 와 을 이해할 수 있다.    언제 실행컨텍스트를 생성했다가 언제 없애는가? 자바스크립트 코드를 실행시키면 자…","html":"<blockquote>\n<p>🔥 실행컨텍스트: 자바스크립트의 동작원리를 담고 있는 핵심 개념</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>실행컨텍스트를 이해하면, 자바스크립트가 스코프를 기반으로 <strong>식별자와 식별자에 바인딩된 값(식별자 바인딩)을 관리하는 방식</strong>과\n<code class=\"language-text\">호이스팅</code>이 발생하는 이유, <code class=\"language-text\">클로저</code>의 동작 방식, 그리고 <code class=\"language-text\">태스크 큐</code>와 함께 동작하는 <code class=\"language-text\">이벤트 핸들러</code>와 <code class=\"language-text\">비동기 처리의 동작 방식</code>을 이해할 수 있다.</p>\n<p><figure class='gatsby-resp-image-figure' style='margin-bottom: 16px;'>\n    <span class='gatsby-resp-image-wrapper' style='position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 680px; '>\n      <a class='gatsby-resp-image-link' href='/static/01e8341d60e41280f92e387eedbdd550/1d917/image.png' style='display: block' target='_blank' rel='noopener'>\n    <span class='gatsby-resp-image-background-image' style=\"padding-bottom: 43.529411764705884%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class='gatsby-resp-image-image' alt='실행컨텍스트: 코드를 실행하는데 필요한 상태를 모아둔 객체' title='' src='/static/01e8341d60e41280f92e387eedbdd550/ca1dc/image.png' srcset='/static/01e8341d60e41280f92e387eedbdd550/e7570/image.png 170w,\n/static/01e8341d60e41280f92e387eedbdd550/f46e7/image.png 340w,\n/static/01e8341d60e41280f92e387eedbdd550/ca1dc/image.png 680w,\n/static/01e8341d60e41280f92e387eedbdd550/02d09/image.png 1020w,\n/static/01e8341d60e41280f92e387eedbdd550/9d567/image.png 1360w,\n/static/01e8341d60e41280f92e387eedbdd550/1d917/image.png 2110w' sizes='(max-width: 680px) 100vw, 680px' style='width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;' loading='lazy' decoding='async'>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class='gatsby-resp-image-figcaption'>실행컨텍스트: 코드를 실행하는데 필요한 상태를 모아둔 객체</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p><figure class='gatsby-resp-image-figure' style='margin-bottom: 16px;'>\n    <span class='gatsby-resp-image-wrapper' style='position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 680px; '>\n      <a class='gatsby-resp-image-link' href='/static/cdc9ccda98487a0adfbf75925132f225/75225/image-1.png' style='display: block' target='_blank' rel='noopener'>\n    <span class='gatsby-resp-image-background-image' style=\"padding-bottom: 31.176470588235293%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class='gatsby-resp-image-image' alt='실행컨텍스트 내부' title='' src='/static/cdc9ccda98487a0adfbf75925132f225/ca1dc/image-1.png' srcset='/static/cdc9ccda98487a0adfbf75925132f225/e7570/image-1.png 170w,\n/static/cdc9ccda98487a0adfbf75925132f225/f46e7/image-1.png 340w,\n/static/cdc9ccda98487a0adfbf75925132f225/ca1dc/image-1.png 680w,\n/static/cdc9ccda98487a0adfbf75925132f225/02d09/image-1.png 1020w,\n/static/cdc9ccda98487a0adfbf75925132f225/75225/image-1.png 1044w' sizes='(max-width: 680px) 100vw, 680px' style='width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;' loading='lazy' decoding='async'>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class='gatsby-resp-image-figcaption'>실행컨텍스트 내부</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p><span class='gatsby-resp-image-wrapper' style='position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 680px; margin-bottom: 16px;'>\n      <a class='gatsby-resp-image-link' href='/static/5f734c6d6e23c900ba3fe441d7c91eb8/112b1/image-2.png' style='display: block' target='_blank' rel='noopener'>\n    <span class='gatsby-resp-image-background-image' style=\"padding-bottom: 24.11764705882353%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class='gatsby-resp-image-image' alt='image 2' title='' src='/static/5f734c6d6e23c900ba3fe441d7c91eb8/ca1dc/image-2.png' srcset='/static/5f734c6d6e23c900ba3fe441d7c91eb8/e7570/image-2.png 170w,\n/static/5f734c6d6e23c900ba3fe441d7c91eb8/f46e7/image-2.png 340w,\n/static/5f734c6d6e23c900ba3fe441d7c91eb8/ca1dc/image-2.png 680w,\n/static/5f734c6d6e23c900ba3fe441d7c91eb8/02d09/image-2.png 1020w,\n/static/5f734c6d6e23c900ba3fe441d7c91eb8/9d567/image-2.png 1360w,\n/static/5f734c6d6e23c900ba3fe441d7c91eb8/112b1/image-2.png 2058w' sizes='(max-width: 680px) 100vw, 680px' style='width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;' loading='lazy' decoding='async'>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h3 id=\"언제-실행컨텍스트를-생성했다가-언제-없애는가\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%96%B8%EC%A0%9C-%EC%8B%A4%ED%96%89%EC%BB%A8%ED%85%8D%EC%8A%A4%ED%8A%B8%EB%A5%BC-%EC%83%9D%EC%84%B1%ED%96%88%EB%8B%A4%EA%B0%80-%EC%96%B8%EC%A0%9C-%EC%97%86%EC%95%A0%EB%8A%94%EA%B0%80\" aria-label=\"언제 실행컨텍스트를 생성했다가 언제 없애는가 permalink\" class=\"heading-anchor before\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"15\" height=\"15\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M6.188 8.719c.439-.439.926-.801 1.444-1.087 2.887-1.591 6.589-.745 8.445 2.069l-2.246 2.245c-.644-1.469-2.243-2.305-3.834-1.949-.599.134-1.168.433-1.633.898l-4.304 4.306c-1.307 1.307-1.307 3.433 0 4.74 1.307 1.307 3.433 1.307 4.74 0l1.327-1.327c1.207.479 2.501.67 3.779.575l-2.929 2.929c-2.511 2.511-6.582 2.511-9.093 0s-2.511-6.582 0-9.093l4.304-4.306zm6.836-6.836l-2.929 2.929c1.277-.096 2.572.096 3.779.574l1.326-1.326c1.307-1.307 3.433-1.307 4.74 0 1.307 1.307 1.307 3.433 0 4.74l-4.305 4.305c-1.311 1.311-3.44 1.3-4.74 0-.303-.303-.564-.68-.727-1.051l-2.246 2.245c.236.358.481.667.796.982.812.812 1.846 1.417 3.036 1.704 1.542.371 3.194.166 4.613-.617.518-.286 1.005-.648 1.444-1.087l4.304-4.305c2.512-2.511 2.512-6.582.001-9.093-2.511-2.51-6.581-2.51-9.092 0z\"/></svg></a>언제 실행컨텍스트를 생성했다가 언제 없애는가?</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>자바스크립트 <strong>코드를 실행시키면</strong> 자바스크립트 엔진은 <code class=\"language-text\">Call Stack</code>이라는 통에 <code class=\"language-text\">전역 실행컨텍스트</code>를 담는다.</li>\n<li>실행컨텍스트니까 안에 아까봤던 <code class=\"language-text\">Record</code>와 <code class=\"language-text\">Outer</code>가 담겨있고\n<code class=\"language-text\">함수 A의 실행 컨텍스트</code>를 생성해서 또 <code class=\"language-text\">Call Stack</code>에 담는다.</li>\n<li>콜스택에서는 가장 최근에 추가된 실행 컨텍스트만 활성화된다.\n만약 함수A에서 함수B가 호출되면 또 실행컨텍스트를 담는다.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><figure class='gatsby-resp-image-figure' style='margin-bottom: 16px;'>\n    <span class='gatsby-resp-image-wrapper' style='position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 680px; '>\n      <a class='gatsby-resp-image-link' href='/static/8794b165d78c51dcc99c21162d75dcdf/018c1/image-4.png' style='display: block' target='_blank' rel='noopener'>\n    <span class='gatsby-resp-image-background-image' style=\"padding-bottom: 73.52941176470587%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class='gatsby-resp-image-image' alt='실행된 순서대로 Call Stack에 쌓이는 실행컨텍스트들' title='' src='/static/8794b165d78c51dcc99c21162d75dcdf/ca1dc/image-4.png' srcset='/static/8794b165d78c51dcc99c21162d75dcdf/e7570/image-4.png 170w,\n/static/8794b165d78c51dcc99c21162d75dcdf/f46e7/image-4.png 340w,\n/static/8794b165d78c51dcc99c21162d75dcdf/ca1dc/image-4.png 680w,\n/static/8794b165d78c51dcc99c21162d75dcdf/02d09/image-4.png 1020w,\n/static/8794b165d78c51dcc99c21162d75dcdf/018c1/image-4.png 1282w' sizes='(max-width: 680px) 100vw, 680px' style='width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;' loading='lazy' decoding='async'>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class='gatsby-resp-image-figcaption'>실행된 순서대로 Call Stack에 쌓이는 실행컨텍스트들</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p>함수B의 실행을 마치고 함수 B가 <strong>종료되면 실행컨텍스트가 사라진다</strong>.\n이어서 함수A가 사라지면 실행컨텍스트도 사라진다.</p>\n<h3 id=\"1-Record로-호이스팅-이해하기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#1-Record%EB%A1%9C-%ED%98%B8%EC%9D%B4%EC%8A%A4%ED%8C%85-%EC%9D%B4%ED%95%B4%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"1 Record로 호이스팅 이해하기 permalink\" class=\"heading-anchor before\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"15\" height=\"15\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M6.188 8.719c.439-.439.926-.801 1.444-1.087 2.887-1.591 6.589-.745 8.445 2.069l-2.246 2.245c-.644-1.469-2.243-2.305-3.834-1.949-.599.134-1.168.433-1.633.898l-4.304 4.306c-1.307 1.307-1.307 3.433 0 4.74 1.307 1.307 3.433 1.307 4.74 0l1.327-1.327c1.207.479 2.501.67 3.779.575l-2.929 2.929c-2.511 2.511-6.582 2.511-9.093 0s-2.511-6.582 0-9.093l4.304-4.306zm6.836-6.836l-2.929 2.929c1.277-.096 2.572.096 3.779.574l1.326-1.326c1.307-1.307 3.433-1.307 4.74 0 1.307 1.307 1.307 3.433 0 4.74l-4.305 4.305c-1.311 1.311-3.44 1.3-4.74 0-.303-.303-.564-.68-.727-1.051l-2.246 2.245c.236.358.481.667.796.982.812.812 1.846 1.417 3.036 1.704 1.542.371 3.194.166 4.613-.617.518-.286 1.005-.648 1.444-1.087l4.304-4.305c2.512-2.511 2.512-6.582.001-9.093-2.511-2.51-6.581-2.51-9.092 0z\"/></svg></a>1. <code class=\"language-text\">Record</code>로 <code class=\"language-text\">호이스팅</code> 이해하기</h3>\n<hr>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"cs\"><pre class=\"language-cs\"><code class=\"language-cs\"><span class=\"token comment\">// var로 선언한 경우</span>\nconsole<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>TVChannel<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// undefined</span>\n<span class=\"token class-name\"><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span></span> TVChannel <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"NetFlix\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nconsole<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>TVChannel<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// netflix</span></code></pre></div>\n<blockquote>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">호이스팅</code>: 선언문이 마치 최상단에 끌어올려진 듯한 현상</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><strong>호이스팅이 발생하는 이유?</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>선언문이 있는 코드라인을 물리적으로 최상단에 끌어올렸기 때문이 아니라,\n자바스크립트 엔진이 먼저 코드를 스캔하면서 <strong>변수같은 정보를 실행컨텍스트 어딘가에\n미리 기록해놓기 때문</strong>이다.</li>\n<li>이때 기록해 놓는 곳이 <code class=\"language-text\">Environment Record</code>이고, <code class=\"language-text\">식별자와 식별자에 바인딩된 값을 기록</code>해두는 객체다.</li>\n<li>이 환경레코드에 <strong>변수가 어떻게 저장되는지만 봐도</strong> 호이스팅을 빠삭하게 이해할 수 있다.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"1-1-Variable-Hoisting-var-let-const\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#1-1-Variable-Hoisting-var-let-const\" aria-label=\"1 1 Variable Hoisting var let const permalink\" class=\"heading-anchor before\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"15\" height=\"15\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M6.188 8.719c.439-.439.926-.801 1.444-1.087 2.887-1.591 6.589-.745 8.445 2.069l-2.246 2.245c-.644-1.469-2.243-2.305-3.834-1.949-.599.134-1.168.433-1.633.898l-4.304 4.306c-1.307 1.307-1.307 3.433 0 4.74 1.307 1.307 3.433 1.307 4.74 0l1.327-1.327c1.207.479 2.501.67 3.779.575l-2.929 2.929c-2.511 2.511-6.582 2.511-9.093 0s-2.511-6.582 0-9.093l4.304-4.306zm6.836-6.836l-2.929 2.929c1.277-.096 2.572.096 3.779.574l1.326-1.326c1.307-1.307 3.433-1.307 4.74 0 1.307 1.307 1.307 3.433 0 4.74l-4.305 4.305c-1.311 1.311-3.44 1.3-4.74 0-.303-.303-.564-.68-.727-1.051l-2.246 2.245c.236.358.481.667.796.982.812.812 1.846 1.417 3.036 1.704 1.542.371 3.194.166 4.613-.617.518-.286 1.005-.648 1.444-1.087l4.304-4.305c2.512-2.511 2.512-6.582.001-9.093-2.511-2.51-6.581-2.51-9.092 0z\"/></svg></a>1-1. Variable Hoisting (var, let, const)</h3>\n<hr>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">Create &amp; Push</code></p>\n<p>전역 실행 컨텍스트 한칸을 생성해서 콜스택에 넣는다.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">Scan &amp; Declare</code> 생성단계 (선언문만 실행해서 환경레코드에 기록)</p>\n<p>전체 코드를 스캔하면서 선언할게 있는지 찾아보고 있다면 먼저 선언해둔다.\n선언하는 과정에는 생성해둔 실행컨텍스트 안에 있는 환경레코드에 새로운 식별자 TV Channel을 기록한다.</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"cs\"><pre class=\"language-cs\"><code class=\"language-cs\"><span class=\"token comment\">// var로 선언한 경우</span>\n <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> TVChannel<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> undefined <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// 선언</span></code></pre></div>\n<ol start=\"3\">\n<li>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">실행단계</code> : 생성단계에서 환경레코드에 <strong>기록해둔 정보를 참조하거나 업데이트</strong></p>\n<p>선언문 외 나머지 코드 순차적 실행</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"cs\"><pre class=\"language-cs\"><code class=\"language-cs\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> TVChanel<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Netflix\"</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// 업데이트해서 할당 (환경레코드에 저장)</span>\nconsole<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> 에서는 환경레코드의 값을 참조</code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"cs\"><pre class=\"language-cs\"><code class=\"language-cs\"><span class=\"token comment\">// let, const로 선언한 경우</span>\nconsole<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>TVChannel<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// ReferenceError -> 일시적 사각지대</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// let, const로 선언했을때 선언 이전에 식별자를 참조할 수 없는 구역</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> TVChannel <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"NetFlix\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nconsole<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>TVChannel<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// netflix</span></code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>let, const로 선언한 경우</strong>\n엔진이 TV Channel <strong>식별자를 기록해두긴 하지만 값을 초기화하지는 않는다.</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"cs\"><pre class=\"language-cs\"><code class=\"language-cs\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> TVChannel <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// 따라서 선언문 이전에 TV Channel을 참조하려고 하면 ReferenceError 발생</span></code></pre></div>\n<blockquote>\n<p><strong>let, const가 선언만 하는 이유</strong>: 선언라인 이전에는 참조할 수 없도록.\n일반적인 프로그래밍 방식을 추구할 수 있도록 '언어차원에서 보완되었다'</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><figure class='gatsby-resp-image-figure' style='margin-bottom: 16px;'>\n    <span class='gatsby-resp-image-wrapper' style='position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 680px; '>\n      <a class='gatsby-resp-image-link' href='/static/1a57df1242d6e7fb36ccee1c7835d078/99dcf/image-5.png' style='display: block' target='_blank' rel='noopener'>\n    <span class='gatsby-resp-image-background-image' style=\"padding-bottom: 33.529411764705884%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class='gatsby-resp-image-image' alt='var키워드의 경우 선언과 초기화가 동시에 이뤄지고, let, const는 선언만 이뤄진다.' title='' src='/static/1a57df1242d6e7fb36ccee1c7835d078/ca1dc/image-5.png' srcset='/static/1a57df1242d6e7fb36ccee1c7835d078/e7570/image-5.png 170w,\n/static/1a57df1242d6e7fb36ccee1c7835d078/f46e7/image-5.png 340w,\n/static/1a57df1242d6e7fb36ccee1c7835d078/ca1dc/image-5.png 680w,\n/static/1a57df1242d6e7fb36ccee1c7835d078/02d09/image-5.png 1020w,\n/static/1a57df1242d6e7fb36ccee1c7835d078/99dcf/image-5.png 1118w' sizes='(max-width: 680px) 100vw, 680px' style='width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;' loading='lazy' decoding='async'>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class='gatsby-resp-image-figcaption'>var키워드의 경우 선언과 초기화가 동시에 이뤄지고, let, const는 선언만 이뤄진다.</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<h3 id=\"1-2-Function-Hoisting\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#1-2-Function-Hoisting\" aria-label=\"1 2 Function Hoisting permalink\" class=\"heading-anchor before\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"15\" height=\"15\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M6.188 8.719c.439-.439.926-.801 1.444-1.087 2.887-1.591 6.589-.745 8.445 2.069l-2.246 2.245c-.644-1.469-2.243-2.305-3.834-1.949-.599.134-1.168.433-1.633.898l-4.304 4.306c-1.307 1.307-1.307 3.433 0 4.74 1.307 1.307 3.433 1.307 4.74 0l1.327-1.327c1.207.479 2.501.67 3.779.575l-2.929 2.929c-2.511 2.511-6.582 2.511-9.093 0s-2.511-6.582 0-9.093l4.304-4.306zm6.836-6.836l-2.929 2.929c1.277-.096 2.572.096 3.779.574l1.326-1.326c1.307-1.307 3.433-1.307 4.74 0 1.307 1.307 1.307 3.433 0 4.74l-4.305 4.305c-1.311 1.311-3.44 1.3-4.74 0-.303-.303-.564-.68-.727-1.051l-2.246 2.245c.236.358.481.667.796.982.812.812 1.846 1.417 3.036 1.704 1.542.371 3.194.166 4.613-.617.518-.286 1.005-.648 1.444-1.087l4.304-4.305c2.512-2.511 2.512-6.582.001-9.093-2.511-2.51-6.581-2.51-9.092 0z\"/></svg></a>1-2. Function Hoisting</h3>\n<ol>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">함수표현식</code>: <strong>변수 호이스팅과 동일하게 동작</strong></li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"cs\"><pre class=\"language-cs\"><code class=\"language-cs\"><span class=\"token function\">study</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// TypeError = undefined는 function이 아님</span>\n<span class=\"token class-name\"><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span></span> study <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// call stack</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> study <span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> undefined <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> 로 저장</code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"cs\"><pre class=\"language-cs\"><code class=\"language-cs\"><span class=\"token function\">study</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// Reference Error:</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> study <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// call stack</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> study <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// 환경레코드에 기록된 값이 없음</span></code></pre></div>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">함수 선언문</code>: 선언과 동시에 <strong>완성된 함수 객체를 생성</strong>해서 <strong>환경 레코드에 기록함</strong>.\n선언라인 전에도 함수를 호출할 수 있다!</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"cs\"><pre class=\"language-cs\"><code class=\"language-cs\"><span class=\"token function\">study</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// 에러없이 실행된다.</span>\n\n<span class=\"token return-type class-name\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">study</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>'study'<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// call stack</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> study<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> f <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p><figure class='gatsby-resp-image-figure' style='margin-bottom: 16px;'>\n    <span class='gatsby-resp-image-wrapper' style='position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 576px; '>\n      <a class='gatsby-resp-image-link' href='/static/18dacd977d09f1d0793513941ab418d5/694da/image-6.png' style='display: block' target='_blank' rel='noopener'>\n    <span class='gatsby-resp-image-background-image' style=\"padding-bottom: 115.29411764705884%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class='gatsby-resp-image-image' alt='개념에 익숙해지자!' title='' src='/static/18dacd977d09f1d0793513941ab418d5/694da/image-6.png' srcset='/static/18dacd977d09f1d0793513941ab418d5/e7570/image-6.png 170w,\n/static/18dacd977d09f1d0793513941ab418d5/f46e7/image-6.png 340w,\n/static/18dacd977d09f1d0793513941ab418d5/694da/image-6.png 576w' sizes='(max-width: 576px) 100vw, 576px' style='width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;' loading='lazy' decoding='async'>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class='gatsby-resp-image-figcaption'>개념에 익숙해지자!</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<h3 id=\"2-Outer-외부환경참조---바깥-Lexical-Environment를-가리킴\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#2-Outer-%EC%99%B8%EB%B6%80%ED%99%98%EA%B2%BD%EC%B0%B8%EC%A1%B0---%EB%B0%94%EA%B9%A5-Lexical-Environment%EB%A5%BC-%EA%B0%80%EB%A6%AC%ED%82%B4\" aria-label=\"2 Outer 외부환경참조   바깥 Lexical Environment를 가리킴 permalink\" class=\"heading-anchor before\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"15\" height=\"15\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M6.188 8.719c.439-.439.926-.801 1.444-1.087 2.887-1.591 6.589-.745 8.445 2.069l-2.246 2.245c-.644-1.469-2.243-2.305-3.834-1.949-.599.134-1.168.433-1.633.898l-4.304 4.306c-1.307 1.307-1.307 3.433 0 4.74 1.307 1.307 3.433 1.307 4.74 0l1.327-1.327c1.207.479 2.501.67 3.779.575l-2.929 2.929c-2.511 2.511-6.582 2.511-9.093 0s-2.511-6.582 0-9.093l4.304-4.306zm6.836-6.836l-2.929 2.929c1.277-.096 2.572.096 3.779.574l1.326-1.326c1.307-1.307 3.433-1.307 4.74 0 1.307 1.307 1.307 3.433 0 4.74l-4.305 4.305c-1.311 1.311-3.44 1.3-4.74 0-.303-.303-.564-.68-.727-1.051l-2.246 2.245c.236.358.481.667.796.982.812.812 1.846 1.417 3.036 1.704 1.542.371 3.194.166 4.613-.617.518-.286 1.005-.648 1.444-1.087l4.304-4.305c2.512-2.511 2.512-6.582.001-9.093-2.511-2.51-6.581-2.51-9.092 0z\"/></svg></a>2. <code class=\"language-text\">Outer</code>: 외부환경참조 - 바깥 Lexical Environment를 가리킴</h3>\n<blockquote>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">Lexical 환경(정적환경)</code>: Record, Outer를 합친 환경</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><figure class='gatsby-resp-image-figure' style='margin-bottom: 16px;'>\n    <span class='gatsby-resp-image-wrapper' style='position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 458px; '>\n      <a class='gatsby-resp-image-link' href='/static/4e6c577c9c1c22cd20bce50386cb4fdb/e5e51/image-7.png' style='display: block' target='_blank' rel='noopener'>\n    <span class='gatsby-resp-image-background-image' style=\"padding-bottom: 46.470588235294116%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class='gatsby-resp-image-image' alt='렉시컬환경' title='' src='/static/4e6c577c9c1c22cd20bce50386cb4fdb/e5e51/image-7.png' srcset='/static/4e6c577c9c1c22cd20bce50386cb4fdb/e7570/image-7.png 170w,\n/static/4e6c577c9c1c22cd20bce50386cb4fdb/f46e7/image-7.png 340w,\n/static/4e6c577c9c1c22cd20bce50386cb4fdb/e5e51/image-7.png 458w' sizes='(max-width: 458px) 100vw, 458px' style='width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;' loading='lazy' decoding='async'>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class='gatsby-resp-image-figcaption'>렉시컬환경</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"cs\"><pre class=\"language-cs\"><code class=\"language-cs\"><span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> lamp <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">false</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token return-type class-name\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">goTo2F</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> lamp <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">true</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>lamp<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// ?</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">goTo2F</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<p><figure class='gatsby-resp-image-figure' style='margin-bottom: 16px;'>\n    <span class='gatsby-resp-image-wrapper' style='position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 680px; '>\n      <a class='gatsby-resp-image-link' href='/static/7e5278406fffe6e71deae3e8aa01d469/97114/image-8.png' style='display: block' target='_blank' rel='noopener'>\n    <span class='gatsby-resp-image-background-image' style=\"padding-bottom: 81.17647058823529%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class='gatsby-resp-image-image' alt='console의 lamp는 어떤 값이 될까?' title='' src='/static/7e5278406fffe6e71deae3e8aa01d469/ca1dc/image-8.png' srcset='/static/7e5278406fffe6e71deae3e8aa01d469/e7570/image-8.png 170w,\n/static/7e5278406fffe6e71deae3e8aa01d469/f46e7/image-8.png 340w,\n/static/7e5278406fffe6e71deae3e8aa01d469/ca1dc/image-8.png 680w,\n/static/7e5278406fffe6e71deae3e8aa01d469/97114/image-8.png 690w' sizes='(max-width: 680px) 100vw, 680px' style='width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;' loading='lazy' decoding='async'>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class='gatsby-resp-image-figcaption'>console의 lamp는 어떤 값이 될까?</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<ul>\n<li>이런 상황에서 <strong>함수나 변수의 값을 결정</strong>해내는 것을 <code class=\"language-text\">식별자 결정</code>이라 한다.</li>\n<li>자바스크립트 엔진이 어떻게 <code class=\"language-text\">outer를 활용</code>해서 의사결정을 하는지 알아보자</li>\n</ul>\n<p><span class='gatsby-resp-image-wrapper' style='position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 666px; margin-bottom: 16px;'>\n      <a class='gatsby-resp-image-link' href='/static/8077b0fbe5b7d391062031c94d539b02/934f0/image-9.png' style='display: block' target='_blank' rel='noopener'>\n    <span class='gatsby-resp-image-background-image' style=\"padding-bottom: 67.64705882352942%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class='gatsby-resp-image-image' alt='image 9' title='' src='/static/8077b0fbe5b7d391062031c94d539b02/934f0/image-9.png' srcset='/static/8077b0fbe5b7d391062031c94d539b02/e7570/image-9.png 170w,\n/static/8077b0fbe5b7d391062031c94d539b02/f46e7/image-9.png 340w,\n/static/8077b0fbe5b7d391062031c94d539b02/934f0/image-9.png 666w' sizes='(max-width: 666px) 100vw, 666px' style='width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;' loading='lazy' decoding='async'>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<ol>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">goTo2F();</code> 가 실행된다고 생각해보자.\n함수의 실행컨텍스트를 새로 생성하고\n이때 자바스크립트 엔진은 새로 생성된 실행컨텍스트에\n바깥 <code class=\"language-text\">렉시컬환경</code>으로 돌아갈 수 있는 outer를 남겨놓는다.</li>\n<li>이제 필요한 경우 바깥 환경레코드에 저장된 식별자도 참조할 수 있게 되었다.</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"cs\"><pre class=\"language-cs\"><code class=\"language-cs\"><span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> lamp <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">false</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token return-type class-name\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">goTo2F</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> lamp <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">true</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>lamp<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// ?</span>\n  <span class=\"token return-type class-name\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">goTo3F</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> pet <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> 'puppy'<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>pet<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// puppy</span>\n    console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>corona<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// ReferenceError</span>\n    console<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>lamp<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// true</span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\">// 2층의 lamp가 있기 때문에 1층의 lamp는 가려진다.</span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\">// ✅ 변수 섀도잉</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  <span class=\"token function\">goTo3F</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">goTo2F</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>✅ <code class=\"language-text\">변수 섀도잉</code>: <strong>동일한 식별자</strong>로 인해 상위 스코프에서 선언된 식별자의 값이 가려지는 현상</p>\n<p>✅ <code class=\"language-text\">스코프체인</code>: 식별자를 결정할 때 활용하는 <strong>스코프의 연결 리스트</strong></p>\n<p>✅ <code class=\"language-text\">스코프체이닝</code>: 식별자를 결정하기 위해 <strong>타고타고 가서 결정하는 것</strong> 자체</p>\n<p><span class='gatsby-resp-image-wrapper' style='position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 680px; margin-bottom: 16px;'>\n      <a class='gatsby-resp-image-link' href='/static/572e168b7a7b6a74a734e9bfeab8c03b/4cff2/image-10.png' style='display: block' target='_blank' rel='noopener'>\n    <span class='gatsby-resp-image-background-image' style=\"padding-bottom: 63.52941176470588%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class='gatsby-resp-image-image' alt='image 10' title='' src='/static/572e168b7a7b6a74a734e9bfeab8c03b/ca1dc/image-10.png' srcset='/static/572e168b7a7b6a74a734e9bfeab8c03b/e7570/image-10.png 170w,\n/static/572e168b7a7b6a74a734e9bfeab8c03b/f46e7/image-10.png 340w,\n/static/572e168b7a7b6a74a734e9bfeab8c03b/ca1dc/image-10.png 680w,\n/static/572e168b7a7b6a74a734e9bfeab8c03b/02d09/image-10.png 1020w,\n/static/572e168b7a7b6a74a734e9bfeab8c03b/9d567/image-10.png 1360w,\n/static/572e168b7a7b6a74a734e9bfeab8c03b/4cff2/image-10.png 1404w' sizes='(max-width: 680px) 100vw, 680px' style='width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;' loading='lazy' decoding='async'>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h3 id=\"3-실행컨텍스트-정리\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#3-%EC%8B%A4%ED%96%89%EC%BB%A8%ED%85%8D%EC%8A%A4%ED%8A%B8-%EC%A0%95%EB%A6%AC\" aria-label=\"3 실행컨텍스트 정리 permalink\" class=\"heading-anchor before\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"15\" height=\"15\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M6.188 8.719c.439-.439.926-.801 1.444-1.087 2.887-1.591 6.589-.745 8.445 2.069l-2.246 2.245c-.644-1.469-2.243-2.305-3.834-1.949-.599.134-1.168.433-1.633.898l-4.304 4.306c-1.307 1.307-1.307 3.433 0 4.74 1.307 1.307 3.433 1.307 4.74 0l1.327-1.327c1.207.479 2.501.67 3.779.575l-2.929 2.929c-2.511 2.511-6.582 2.511-9.093 0s-2.511-6.582 0-9.093l4.304-4.306zm6.836-6.836l-2.929 2.929c1.277-.096 2.572.096 3.779.574l1.326-1.326c1.307-1.307 3.433-1.307 4.74 0 1.307 1.307 1.307 3.433 0 4.74l-4.305 4.305c-1.311 1.311-3.44 1.3-4.74 0-.303-.303-.564-.68-.727-1.051l-2.246 2.245c.236.358.481.667.796.982.812.812 1.846 1.417 3.036 1.704 1.542.371 3.194.166 4.613-.617.518-.286 1.005-.648 1.444-1.087l4.304-4.305c2.512-2.511 2.512-6.582.001-9.093-2.511-2.51-6.581-2.51-9.092 0z\"/></svg></a>3. 실행컨텍스트 정리</h3>\n<hr>\n<h4 id=\"식별자-결정을-더욱-효율적으로-하기-위한-수단으로써-필요한-정보를-한데-모아-제공하는-객체\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%8B%9D%EB%B3%84%EC%9E%90-%EA%B2%B0%EC%A0%95%EC%9D%84-%EB%8D%94%EC%9A%B1-%ED%9A%A8%EC%9C%A8%EC%A0%81%EC%9C%BC%EB%A1%9C-%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0-%EC%9C%84%ED%95%9C-%EC%88%98%EB%8B%A8%EC%9C%BC%EB%A1%9C%EC%8D%A8-%ED%95%84%EC%9A%94%ED%95%9C-%EC%A0%95%EB%B3%B4%EB%A5%BC-%ED%95%9C%EB%8D%B0-%EB%AA%A8%EC%95%84-%EC%A0%9C%EA%B3%B5%ED%95%98%EB%8A%94-%EA%B0%9D%EC%B2%B4\" aria-label=\"식별자 결정을 더욱 효율적으로 하기 위한 수단으로써 필요한 정보를 한데 모아 제공하는 객체 permalink\" class=\"heading-anchor before\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"15\" height=\"15\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M6.188 8.719c.439-.439.926-.801 1.444-1.087 2.887-1.591 6.589-.745 8.445 2.069l-2.246 2.245c-.644-1.469-2.243-2.305-3.834-1.949-.599.134-1.168.433-1.633.898l-4.304 4.306c-1.307 1.307-1.307 3.433 0 4.74 1.307 1.307 3.433 1.307 4.74 0l1.327-1.327c1.207.479 2.501.67 3.779.575l-2.929 2.929c-2.511 2.511-6.582 2.511-9.093 0s-2.511-6.582 0-9.093l4.304-4.306zm6.836-6.836l-2.929 2.929c1.277-.096 2.572.096 3.779.574l1.326-1.326c1.307-1.307 3.433-1.307 4.74 0 1.307 1.307 1.307 3.433 0 4.74l-4.305 4.305c-1.311 1.311-3.44 1.3-4.74 0-.303-.303-.564-.68-.727-1.051l-2.246 2.245c.236.358.481.667.796.982.812.812 1.846 1.417 3.036 1.704 1.542.371 3.194.166 4.613-.617.518-.286 1.005-.648 1.444-1.087l4.304-4.305c2.512-2.511 2.512-6.582.001-9.093-2.511-2.51-6.581-2.51-9.092 0z\"/></svg></a>식별자 결정을 더욱 효율적으로 하기 위한 수단으로써, 필요한 정보를 한데 모아 제공하는 객체</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>ES3 에서는 함수가 <strong>어디에서 호출되느냐</strong>에 따라 스코프가 달라졌다.</li>\n<li>함수가 호출될 때마다 동적으로 <strong>그에 걸맞는 스코프를 생성하고 스코프 체인을 연결해 주어야 했다.</strong></li>\n<li>ES5에 들어서는 식별자 결정을 위한 매커니즘이 변경되었다.</li>\n<li><strong>실행컨텍스트라는 하나의 덩어리, 하나의 묶음으로 관리</strong>하도록</li>\n<li>스코프가 호출되는 위치와 상관없이 <strong>어디에 선언되어있느냐에 따라 정적으로 결정</strong>되고</li>\n<li>하나의 컨텍스트 개념으로 묶어놨기 때문에 자바스크립트 엔진은 더욱 <strong>빠르고 효율적으로 식별자를 결정</strong>할 수 있게 되었다.</li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"title":"23. 실행컨텍스트","date":"August 22, 2024","update":"August 22, 2024","tags":["Javascript"],"series":"모던 자바스크립트 Deep Dive"},"fields":{"slug":"/deep-js-23/","readingTime":{"minutes":9.345}}},"seriesList":{"edges":[{"node":{"id":"0f1a2f58-f0a9-551f-a3af-8313370fd034","fields":{"slug":"/deep-js-0/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"0. 프로그래밍"}}},{"node":{"id":"29f780e8-ee3e-58f9-94d1-7d65223be027","fields":{"slug":"/deep-js-1/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"1. 자바스크립트의 기본 개념과 동작원리"}}},{"node":{"id":"300acb14-db5c-57a2-a557-c5569308b991","fields":{"slug":"/deep-js-2/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"2. 자바스크립트 개발 환경과 실행 방법"}}},{"node":{"id":"3c8acf66-3cdd-511c-b852-adbc4d17e6bb","fields":{"slug":"/deep-js-4/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"4. 변수(Variable)"}}},{"node":{"id":"564da37b-b3d6-532f-8046-f1f1c494d18a","fields":{"slug":"/deep-js-5/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"5. 표현식과 문(Expression, Statement)"}}},{"node":{"id":"997615c1-0020-5443-ac34-1148e2930599","fields":{"slug":"/deep-js-6/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"6. 데이터 타입"}}},{"node":{"id":"0dfe45a9-0b33-517c-a55c-f5f5c8b28140","fields":{"slug":"/deep-js-7/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"7. 연산자(Operator)"}}},{"node":{"id":"0376d6f2-f085-5524-b81f-3d30a3fe9bb1","fields":{"slug":"/deep-js-8/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"8. 제어문(Control flow statement)"}}},{"node":{"id":"edd87130-aec4-5180-952d-01faf33d160e","fields":{"slug":"/deep-js-9/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"9. 타입 변환과 단축 평가(Type Coercion)"}}},{"node":{"id":"cc019850-07c7-59bc-b7ec-f6562d751ba8","fields":{"slug":"/deep-js-10/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"10. 객체 리터럴 (Object Literal)"}}},{"node":{"id":"a95a6396-75bf-573d-880b-b619202c1d7d","fields":{"slug":"/deep-js-11/"},"frontmatter":{"